 and jaundice.', 'Synergism', 'Interferon alfa-n1, Oprelvekin, Elapegademase, Peginterferon alfa-2a, Interferon alfacon-1, Histamine, Pegademase, Peginterferon alfa-2b, Glatiramer', 'Pertuzumab, Olaparib, Rucaparib, Tisagenlecleucel, Aminolevulinic acid, Omacetaxine mepesuccinate, Tazemetostat, Altretamine, Enasidenib, Belzutifan, Mitotane, More', 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/134126/', '[1] "Product Information. Plegridy (peginterferon beta-1a)." Biogen Idec Inc, Cambridge, MA.[2] "Product Information. Betaseron (interferon beta-1b)." Berlex, Richmond, CA.[3] "Product Information. Rebif (interferon beta-1a)." Serono Laboratories Inc, Norwell, MA.[4] "Product Information. Avonex (interferon beta-1a)." Biogen, Cambridge, MA.', 1767369485);
